                  <summary><p>Paper manuscript from the UVSL [11/73]. One poem per right page, notes (And occasionally poem ends) on left page. Scriptio continua without line break and cīr split, directly followed by kiḷavi; author and poem number in Tamil in separate line.</p>
<p>Incomplete: KV + 1–399 (AN 7, 317, 322 missing).</p>
<p>Bears testimony to readings from both basic strands (mostly TT, NL, C1+6, corrected by C2+3, but for Maṇimiṭaipavaḷam partly the other way round) plus some additional variations that might be quotations or conjectures.</p></summary>
                  
